725585f-a.title: Queens: 69th Street - 61st Place
725585f-a.text:
69th Street, east side, north of 61st Place, showing in the
foreground the Herte house of About 1875. E. Livey was the owner
in 1873 and Wrnst Norge in 1923.
April 1923.
